        <!-- 8. H2-3 Compare sources -->
        <h2 id="compare" class={h2}>Breeder vs Marketplace vs Rescue vs Pet Store: Side by Side</h2>
        <p class={p}>If you only look at one thing on this page, make it this comparison. It's the block competitors leave out — most tell you where you <em>can</em> buy without ever telling you how the sources actually stack up on the things that decide whether you're happy in a year: price, scam risk, health record and trust. Read across the row and the safe choice tends to make itself.</p>

        <figure class="m-0 my-6">
          <img src={igSource.src} srcset={igSource.srcset} sizes={igSource.sizes} width="1200" height="655" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-stone-200" alt="Breeder versus online marketplace versus rescue versus pet store compared across price, scam risk, health record and overall trust" title="Where to buy an African Grey — source comparison | C.A.Gs" />
