        <h2 id="available" class={h2}>See Our Available Hand-Raised Greys</h2>
        <p class={p}>Here are the African Greys available now — each one hand-raised in Midland, Texas, PCR DNA-sexed, vet-checked and CITES-documented, at one fair, fixed price with nothing hidden behind it. Every card shows exactly what you'd verify on a live call before reserving with a $200 deposit.</p>
